        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Netflix 新订阅无法再选 Basic 　香港暂未受影响</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/02/netflix-is-setting-new-standards-the-end-of-the-basic-subscription-is-approaching/movie-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=netflix-is-setting-new-standards-the-end-of-the-basic-subscription-is-approaching</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/02/netflix-is-setting-new-standards-the-end-of-the-basic-subscription-is-approaching/movie-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:45:35 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影视娱乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Netflix]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1232864</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前串流平台巨头 Netflix 公布 2024 年首季业绩，尽管订阅人数、营收或获利均超出预期（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/19/netflix-17/movie-2/">相关报道</a>），但近日外国有网民就表示 Netflix 取消了最便宜无广告的「Basic 」基本方案，要求他在订阅期结束后改为选择更贵的方案。</p><p>Reddit 用户 <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/RKDreddit/">@RKDreddit</a> 日前分享了一封来自 Netflix 的电邮，要求他在今期订阅结束后升级更贵的方案，倘若订阅期结束后一个月内 @RKDreddit 没有选择新方案，Netflix 会终止其会员。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232866" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/netflixisdiscontinui-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/netflixisdiscontinui-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/netflixisdiscontinui.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/mildlyinfuriating/comments/1cgde33/netflix_is_discontinuing_its_most_popular_and/">RKDreddit@Reddit</a></p><p>@RDKreddit 另外亦上传了一张萤幕截图，可见 Netflix 已经取消最便宜无广告的「Basic」方案，如果用户不想看广告，就要升级至 16.49 美元（约港币 129 元）的「Standard」方案，或者是选择 5.99 美元（约港币 47 元）的有广告「Standard with ads」方案。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232867" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/netflixisdiscontinui-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/netflixisdiscontinui-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/netflixisdiscontinui-1.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/mildlyinfuriating/comments/1cgde33/netflix_is_discontinuing_its_most_popular_and/">RKDreddit@Reddit</a></p><p>截止今日（5 月 2 日）下午 1 时，香港 Netflix 仍然提供基本方案。值得留意的是，香港 Netflix 上月亦调整了订阅费用：</p><p>高级 4K+HDR $93→$108（加幅：16%）</p><p>标准 1080p $78→$88（加幅：12.8%）</p><p>基本 720p $63→$73（加幅：15.9%）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232868" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240502131022-408x580.jpg" alt="" width="408" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240502131022-408x580.jpg 408w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240502131022.jpg 633w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 408px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://help.netflix.com/zh-tw/node/24926">Netflix</a></p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/765/528.htm">IT Home</a>、<a href="https://www.breakinglatest.news/technology/netflix-is-setting-new-standards-the-end-of-the-basic-subscription-is-approaching/">Breaking Latest News</a>、<a href="https://help.netflix.com/zh-tw/node/24926">Netflix</a><br /><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/19/netflix-17/movie-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Netflix 打击共享密码取得成功，首季订阅人数激增超预期</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/08/netflix-16/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Netflix 香港加价 4K 计划加 $15 变每月 $108</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/05/disney-will-crack-down-on-password-sharing-in-june/movie-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Disney+ 6 月起严打共用帐户    CEO：Netflix 是串流媒体领域的标准</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/02/netflix-is-setting-new-standards-the-end-of-the-basic-subscription-is-approaching/movie-2/">Netflix 新订阅无法再选 Basic 　香港暂未受影响</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
